by Andy van Dongen

Features:

* watches incoming pulses from the opto sensors attached to the electricity,
  gas and water meter
* total pulses per meter is measured
* moving sum last 5 minutes per meter is measured
* moving sum last hour per meter is measured
* values are stored in e-eprom in case of power failure
* measurements are reported over radio to a central node

See http://forum.jeelabs.net/node/353#comment-2066
